OL,3,CBomb scene 'like something from
OL,4,CVietnam war'
OL,6,FA part time fire officer has told the
OL,7,FOmagh bomb inquiry when he arrived at
OL,8,Fthe scene of the atrocity it was like
OL,9,Fsomething from the Vietnam war, it was
OL,10,Fa "horror show," he said.
OL,12,FAt the time Paddy Quinn was a retained
OL,13,Fofficer and is now a temporary
OL,14,Fcommander. He was working in the
OL,15,Fcarpet shop he owned when the
OL,16,Fexplosion happened in 1998.
OL,18,F"I now have a permanent photograph in
OL,19,Fmy head," he said.
