OL,3,CBomb scene 'like something from
OL,4,CVietnam war'
OL,6,F"The thought I had looked like when I
OL,7,Fhad seen a photograph many years ago
OL,8,Fof the Vietnam war. There was a cloud
OL,9,Fof dust and there was a young girl
OL,10,Frunning across the road terrified."
OL,12,FHe described the scene as "total
OL,13,Fchaos, devastation and carnage".
OL,15,FThe inquiry at the Strule Arts Centre
OL,16,Fin the Co Tyrone town is continuing to
OL,17,Fhear personal statements from
OL,18,Fwitnesses and people affected by the
OL,19,FReal IRA bombing in 1998.
