OL,6,FThe public inquiry was set up by the
OL,7,FGovernment to examine whether the
OL,8,Fexplosion, which killed 29 people,
OL,9,Fincluding the mother of unborn twins,
OL,10,Fcould have been prevented by the UK
OL,11,Fauthorities.
OL,13,FThis is the first time Mr Quinn has
OL,14,Fopenly spoken about what he witnessed
OL,15,Fthat day on 15 August 1998.
OL,17,FHe told the inquiry he had never
OL,18,Fexplained to his wife what he saw to
OL,19,Fprotect his family.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
