OL,3,CBomb scene 'like something from
OL,4,CVietnam war'
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard how fire crews
OL,7,Ffrantically searched for those injured
OL,8,Fwho may have been trapped in the
OL,9,Frubble.
OL,11,FHe recalled finding someone he knew,
OL,12,FLibby Rush. She was dead.
OL,14,FMr Quinn said when people phoned him
OL,15,Fthe days after the bomb to ask how he
OL,16,Fwas and he would say "I'm fine".
OL,18,F"But what they wouldn't see behind the
OL,19,Fphone I was breaking down and crying,"
OL,20,Fhe continued.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
