OL,6,F"And didn't cry before that. I didn't
OL,7,Fcry at anything. But this was
OL,8,Fdifferent. I didn't know why I was
OL,9,Fcrying. It was just happening because
OL,10,Fof this horror."
OL,12,FPaddy Quinn also said that some of the
OL,13,Ffire fighters had worse experiences
OL,14,Fthan him.
OL,16,FOne lost a member of his family and
OL,17,Fsome to this day still need support
OL,18,Ffor what they experienced.
